    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some minor staining, though the cabin remains functional and smoke-free. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, but buyers should expect the typical maintenance needs associated with a well-used vehicle. It is a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a newer model.",
