      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who needs a great ride without the brand-new price tag! It looks sharp, drives smoothly, and I've made sure to keep up with the basics so it's ready to hit the road. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin. I'm sure you'll see why I've enjoyed it so much!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the M96 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The powertrain delivers a linear torque curve and exceptional throttle response, recently bolstered by an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh clutch assembly. The chassis geometry remains precise, utilizing the factory multi-link rear suspension to provide superior mechanical grip and communicative handling through the corners. It retains its original staggered alloy wheels and features an optional limited-slip differential for enhanced power delivery. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity is robust, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a cooling system optimized with a low-temperature thermostat.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. No major issues.",
